        "content": {
          "work": {
            "entries": [
              {
                "id": "286ca64e-9ab1-4d32-9905-0996d5d6a5c1",
                "employer": "MV Clouds",
                "isHidden": false,
                "jobTitle": "Salesforce Developer",
                "location": "Ahmedabad, India",
                "createdAt": "2026-03-13T09:06:22.566Z",
                "updatedAt": "2026-03-26T12:20:26.146Z",
                "endDateNew": "04/2025",
                "description": "\u003Cul\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAgentforce and AI integration: Configured Agentforce AI agents with custom actions and REST API interfaces enabling real-time access to third-party systems, applying the same architectural review discipline to AI-generated outputs as to hand-written code.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAI-assisted engineering: Adopted AI coding assistants to accelerate Apex and LWC development cycles while taking full ownership of architecture validation, performance review against Salesforce governor limits, and security best practices across all generated code.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003ELow-code and system orchestration: Built complex Salesforce Flows for rapid process automation alongside pro-code Apex triggers, selecting the right tool for each scenario; experienced in low-code-first thinking for system integration and workflow orchestration.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAgentforce Actions and REST API integrations: Designed and implemented REST API callouts and custom Apex actions enabling Salesforce AI agents to read from and write to external systems in real time, including HomeAdvisor (lead ingestion), QuickBooks (financial sync), and an aerospace parts inventory platform.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAppExchange managed package: Built and published a production package through Salesforce's full security review cycle, enforcing 85%+ Apex test coverage via automated test suites and code reviews; authored documentation and marketing materials for the listing.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EConstruction Management System: Delivered a Service Cloud platform for a client in the construction sector using LWC, Aura, Flows, and QuickBooks integration; worked end-to-end from requirements scoping with the client through to go-live and post-deployment support.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECustom Form Builder: Engineered a zero-code form creation tool (LWC + Apex) with configurable parent-child object relationships up to 3 levels, reducing form creation time from hours to under 10 minutes. Integrated an Einstein Chatbot for automated customer support.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003EInventory Management System: Identified automation potential in a client's stock management process and designed a Service Cloud solution with threshold-based restocking triggers, automated alerts, and real-time supply chain dashboards.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECI/CD and code quality: Owned the team's GitHub-integrated Jenkins CI/CD pipeline, acting as deployment quality gate; enforced code review standards and automated testing across all releases, reducing average deployment time by approximately 40%.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/li\u003E\u003C/ul\u003E",
                "employerLink": "",
                "startDateNew": "02/2023",
                "showPlaceholder": false
              },
